# Spinor.Dirac

Dirac spinors.

A Dirac spinor is a pair of a left-Weyl and a right-Weyl spinor, forming a
4-component object:
  Ψ = (ψ_α, χ̄^α̇)

The Dirac equation in curved or flat spacetime, chirality projectors, and the
relation to Majorana spinors are developed here.

